C'est la fin de l'architecture système pour le Convertisseur de devises.

I'll create a production-ready React 19 frontend for the currency converter with TypeScript, focusing on a clean, card-centered UI with real-time conversion capabilities. Here's the complete implementation:

## File Structure
```
