# Architecture Overview: Todo Application

## Folder Structure

```
todo-app/
├── backend/                  # FastAPI backend
│   ├── main.py               # FastAPI app initialization
│   ├── models.py             # Pydantic models
│   ├── schemas.py            # Data transfer schemas
