```txt api_contracts.md
# API Contracts: Todo Application

## Base URL
```
http://localhost:8000
```

## Endpoints

### Task Endpoints

#### Create a Task
```
POST /tasks/
```
- **Request Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "title": "Buy groceries",
    "description": "Milk, eggs, bread"
  }
  ```
- **Response** (201 Created):
  ```json
  {
    "id": 1,
    "title": "Buy groceries",
    "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
    "status": "pending"
  }
  ```

#### Get All Tasks
```
GET /tasks/
```
- **Response** (200 OK):
  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Buy groceries",
      "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
      "status": "pending"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Walk the dog",
      "description": null,
      "status": "completed"
    }
  ]
  ```

#### Get a Task by ID
```
GET /tasks/{task_id}
```
- **Parameters**:
  - `task_id` (path parameter): ID of the task
- **Response** (200 OK):
  ```json
  {
    "id": 1,
    "title": "Buy groceries",
    "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
    "status": "pending"
  }
  ```
- **Error Response** (404 Not Found):
  ```json
  {
    "detail": "Task not found"
  }
  ```

#### Update a Task
```
PUT /tasks/{task_id}
```
- **Parameters**:
  - `task_id` (path parameter): ID of the task
- **Request Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "status": "completed"
  }
  ```
- **Response** (200 OK):
  ```json
  {
    "id": 1,
    "title": "Buy groceries",
    "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
    "status": "completed"
  }
  ```
- **Error Response** (404 Not Found):
  ```json
  {
    "detail": "Task not found"
  }
  ```

#### Delete a Task
```
DELETE /tasks/{task_id}
```
- **Parameters**:
  - `task_id` (path parameter): ID of the task
- **Response** (204 No Content): Empty response
- **Error Response** (404 Not Found):
  ```json
  {
    "detail": "Task not found"
  }
  ```

#### Filter Tasks by Status
```
GET /tasks/filter/{status}
```
- **Parameters**:
  - `status` (path parameter): Task status to filter by (`pending` or `completed`)
- **Response** (200 OK):
  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Buy groceries",
      "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
      "status": "pending"
    }
  ]
  ```

### Health Endpoint

#### Health Check
```
GET /health
```
- **Response** (200 OK):
  ```json
  {
    "status": "healthy"
  }
  ```
